title: Mike Russo in for PA #92Noon - Boudreau, LaPanta, Graff, Cronin
description: Mike Russo is in for PA this morning, joined by Anthony LaPanta in the first hour. They talk with head coach Bruce Boudreau. The Athletic's, Chad Graff and ESPN's, Courtney Cronin talk Vikings in the second and third hour. George Richards from The Athletic Miami and NHL legend, John Torchetti call in.
